### Crear Panel Vidrio
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/catalog/item-types
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Panel Vidrio",
  "description": "Paneles de vidrio templado",
  "schemaDefinition": "{\"fields\":[{\"name\":\"largo\",\"type\":\"decimal\",\"unit\":\"mm\"},{\"name\":\"ancho\",\"type\":\"decimal\",\"unit\":\"mm\"},{\"name\":\"espesor\",\"type\":\"decimal\",\"unit\":\"mm\"}]}"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("typeId", response.body.id);
%}

### Crear Soporte Personalizado
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/catalog/item-types
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Soporte Personalizado",
  "description": "Soportes fabricados a medida",
  "schemaDefinition": "{\"fields\":[{\"name\":\"alto\",\"type\":\"decimal\",\"unit\":\"mm\"},{\"name\":\"ancho\",\"type\":\"decimal\",\"unit\":\"mm\"},{\"name\":\"material\",\"type\":\"string\"}]}"
}

### Listar tipos
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/catalog/item-types?page=0&size=20
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### Obtener tipo por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/catalog/item-types/{{typeId}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### Actualizar tipo
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/catalog/item-types/{{typeId}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Panel Vidrio Templado",
  "description": "Actualizado: paneles de vidrio templado",
  "schemaDefinition": "{\"fields\":[{\"name\":\"largo\",\"type\":\"decimal\",\"unit\":\"mm\"},{\"name\":\"ancho\",\"type\":\"decimal\",\"unit\":\"mm\"},{\"name\":\"espesor\",\"type\":\"decimal\",\"unit\":\"mm\"},{\"name\":\"tinte\",\"type\":\"string\"}]}"
}

### Eliminar tipo
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/catalog/item-types/{{typeId}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
